name: Phuong Nguyen Apartment - Keangnam Hanoi
address: A4501 Buidling A Keangnam, Street Pham Hung, Tu Liem District, Cau Giay District, Hanoi, Vietnam
hotelDesc:
Set in Ðinh Thôn, this air-conditioned apartment features free WiFi and a balcony. The property is 8 km from Hanoi and private parking is offered.

A fridge and a stovetop can be found in the kitchen. A flat-screen TV with cable channels is featured. Other facilities at Phuong Nguyen Apartment - Keangnam Hanoi include a fitness centre and year-round outdoor pool.

The nearest airport is Noi Bai International Airport, 22 km from the property.
